        <updateDate>2022-11-03T17:25:26Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Hydrogen Infrastructure Finance and Innovation Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy (DOE) to establish a hydrogen infrastructure finance and innovation pilot program. Under the program, DOE must provide grants and low-interest loans to certain entities for hydrogen infrastructure, including projects for hydrogen transportation, storage, or delivery.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
